{"title":"GitHub + Hexo 搭建博客","date":"2020-11-07T07:45:16.364Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年11月7日","L":"2020/11/07","MM-DD":"11-07"},"link":"2020/11/07/hexo搭建博客","updated":"2020-11-07T11:06:02.117Z","content":"<p>这是我一边搭建一边写的，按照步骤来应该没什么问题</p>\n<h2 id=\"1.准备环境\">1.准备环境<a title=\"#1.准备环境\" href=\"#1.准备环境\"></a></h2>\n<h4 id=\"安装git\">安装git<a title=\"#安装git\" href=\"#安装git\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>去官网下载安装就行</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"安装node\">安装node<a title=\"#安装node\" href=\"#安装node\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>去官网下载安装</strong></p>\n<h4 id=\"安装hexo-cli\">安装hexo-cli<a title=\"#安装hexo-cli\" href=\"#安装hexo-cli\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g // 现在npm和node都是绑定安装</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2.本地安装hexo\">2.本地安装Hexo<a title=\"#2.本地安装hexo\" href=\"#2.本地安装hexo\"></a></h2>\n<h4 id=\"2.1搭建hexo\">2.1搭建hexo<a title=\"#2.1搭建hexo\" href=\"#2.1搭建hexo\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>找一个目录新建一个文件夹用于存放你的blog项目</strong></p>\n<p><strong>打开控制台，cd到你的文件夹下</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/2.1.png\" alt class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"2.2初始化项目\">2.2初始化项目<a title=\"#2.2初始化项目\" href=\"#2.2初始化项目\"></a></h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>初始化项目后通过一下命令就可以在本地访问了</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/2.2.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107141639\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3.创建github仓库\">3.创建GitHub仓库<a title=\"#3.创建github仓库\" href=\"#3.创建github仓库\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/3.1.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107141422\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"4.将github仓库与hexo项目连接起来\">4.将GitHub仓库与hexo项目连接起来<a title=\"#4.将github仓库与hexo项目连接起来\" href=\"#4.将github仓库与hexo项目连接起来\"></a></h2>\n<h4 id=\"4.1-生成ssh密钥\">4.1 生成ssh密钥<a title=\"#4.1-生成ssh密钥\" href=\"#4.1-生成ssh密钥\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>打开控制台输入</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &#x27;github绑定的email&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4.1.1.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107142153\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>生成ssh成功后</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4.1.2.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107152555\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"4.2-设置github\">4.2 设置GitHub<a title=\"#4.2-设置github\" href=\"#4.2-设置github\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>打开GitHub个人设置</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4.2.1.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107142902\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>测试连接GitHub</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4.2.2.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107142648\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"4.3-配置本地hexo项目下的_config.yml\">4.3 配置本地hexo项目下的_config.yml<a title=\"#4.3-配置本地hexo项目下的_config.yml\" href=\"#4.3-配置本地hexo项目下的_config.yml\"></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4.3.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107143151\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"4.4-博客发布到github仓库\">4.4 博客发布到GitHub仓库<a title=\"#4.4-博客发布到github仓库\" href=\"#4.4-博客发布到github仓库\"></a></h4>\n<p><strong>安装依赖</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4.4.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107143638\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>上传GitHub</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo d </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>现在可以直接访问了：<strong><a href=\"http://xn--GitHub-8h6jw94g4v9a.github.io\">GitHub用户名.github.io</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>注意：可能有缓存，要等一会</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"5.配置域名\">5.配置域名<a title=\"#5.配置域名\" href=\"#5.配置域名\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>先买一个域名，要不然还是用GitHub分配给你的域名把</strong></p>\n<p><strong>先ping一下GitHub给你的域名</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.1.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107144754\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>复制ip</strong></p>\n<p><strong>解析域名</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.2.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107145123\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>添加记录</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.3.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107145436\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>创建CNAME文件</strong></p>\n<p><strong>进入你博客目录下的source文件夹，新建一个CNAME文件，将你的域名写进去，CNAME没有后缀名！！</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.4.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107145718\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>重新上传 hexo d</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.5.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107145859\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>现在用你自己的域名应该是上面这张图片的样子</p>\n<p><strong>进入你GitHub仓库的setting下设置一下就好了</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.6.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107150031\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>现在应该可以直接访问了</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Ac-show/blog-images/main/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/5.7.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20201107150046\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n","next":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2020/11/07/hello-world"},"plink":"http://example.com/2020/11/07/hexo搭建博客/","toc":[{"id":"1.准备环境","title":"1.准备环境","index":"1"},{"id":"2.本地安装hexo","title":"2.本地安装Hexo","index":"2"},{"id":"3.创建github仓库","title":"3.创建GitHub仓库","index":"3"},{"id":"4.将github仓库与hexo项目连接起来","title":"4.将GitHub仓库与hexo项目连接起来","index":"4"},{"id":"5.配置域名","title":"5.配置域名","index":"5"}]}